                "thumbnail": "https://www.reuters.com/resizer/QN1_v-bmSiGV_yaXxjVCxS6inyQ=/1200x628/smart/filters:quality(80)/cloudfront-us-east-2.images.arcpublishing.com/reuters/G3ZHSKXWXVN4RIIRETS37QFMZI.jpg",
